{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I bring to you"},{"time":4000,"text":"a message from"},{"time":7000,"text":"tens of thousands of people --"},{"time":10000,"text":"in the villages, in the slums,"},{"time":12000,"text":"in the hinterland of the country --"},{"time":14000,"text":"who have solved problems"},{"time":16000,"text":"through their own genius,"},{"time":18000,"text":"without any"},{"time":20000,"text":"outside help."},{"time":22000,"text":"When our home minister announces"},{"time":25000,"text":"a few weeks ago"},{"time":28000,"text":"a war on"},{"time":30000,"text":"one third of India,"},{"time":32000,"text":"about 200 districts that he mentioned"},{"time":35000,"text":"were ungovernable,"},{"time":37000,"text":"he missed the point."},{"time":40000,"text":"The point that we have been stressing"},{"time":42000,"text":"for the last 21 years,"},{"time":44000,"text":"the point that"},{"time":46000,"text":"people may be economically poor,"},{"time":48000,"text":"but they're not poor in the mind."},{"time":51000,"text":"In other words,"},{"time":53000,"text":"the minds on the margin"},{"time":55000,"text":"are not the marginal minds."},{"time":58000,"text":"That is the message,"},{"time":60000,"text":"which we started 31 years ago."},{"time":62000,"text":"And what did it start?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"Let me just tell you, briefly, my personal journey,"},{"time":66000,"text":"which led me to come to this point."},{"time":69000,"text":"In '85, '86, I was in Bangladesh"},{"time":71000,"text":"advising the government and the research council there"},{"time":73000,"text":"how to help scientists work on the lands,"},{"time":75000,"text":"on the fields of the poor people,"},{"time":78000,"text":"and how to develop research technologies,"},{"time":80000,"text":"which are based on the knowledge of the people."},{"time":84000,"text":"I came back in '86."},{"time":87000,"text":"I had been tremendously invigorated"},{"time":89000,"text":"by the knowledge and creativity that I found in that country,"},{"time":91000,"text":"which had 60 percent landlessness"},{"time":93000,"text":"but amazing creativity."},{"time":96000,"text":"I started looking at my own work:"},{"time":98000,"text":"The work that I had done"},{"time":100000,"text":"for the previous 10 years,"},{"time":102000,"text":"almost every time,"},{"time":104000,"text":"had instances of knowledge"},{"time":106000,"text":"that people had shared."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108000,"text":"Now, I was paid in dollars as a consultant,"},{"time":111000,"text":"and I looked at my income tax return"},{"time":113000,"text":"and tried to ask myself: \"Is there a line in my return,"},{"time":116000,"text":"which shows how much of this income has gone"},{"time":118000,"text":"to the people whose knowledge"},{"time":120000,"text":"has made it possible?"},{"time":122000,"text":"Was it because I'm brilliant"},{"time":124000,"text":"that I'm getting this reward, or because of the revolution?"},{"time":127000,"text":"Is it that I write very well?"},{"time":129000,"text":"Is it that I articulate very well?"},{"time":131000,"text":"Is it that I analyze the data very well?"},{"time":133000,"text":"Is it because I'm a professor, and, therefore,"},{"time":135000,"text":"I must be entitled to this reward from society?\""},{"time":138000,"text":"I tried to convince myself that, \"No, no,"},{"time":140000,"text":"I have worked for the policy changes."},{"time":142000,"text":"You know, the public policy will become"},{"time":144000,"text":"more responsive to the needs of the poor,"},{"time":146000,"text":"and, therefore I think it's okay.\""},{"time":148000,"text":"But it appeared to me"},{"time":151000,"text":"that all these years that I'd been working on exploitation --"},{"time":154000,"text":"exploitation by landlords,"},{"time":156000,"text":"by moneylenders, by traders --"},{"time":159000,"text":"gave me an insight that"},{"time":161000,"text":"probably I was also an exploiter,"},{"time":163000,"text":"because there was no line in my income tax return"},{"time":165000,"text":"which showed this income accrued"},{"time":167000,"text":"because of the brilliance of the people --"},{"time":169000,"text":"those people who have shared their knowledge and good faith and trust with me --"},{"time":171000,"text":"and nothing ever went back to them."},{"time":173000,"text":"So much so, that much of my work till that time"},{"time":175000,"text":"was in the English language."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"The majority of the people from whom I learned didn't know English."},{"time":180000,"text":"So what kind of a contributor was I?"},{"time":182000,"text":"I was talking about social justice,"},{"time":184000,"text":"and here I was, a professional"},{"time":186000,"text":"who was pursuing the most unjust act --"},{"time":188000,"text":"of taking knowledge from the people, making them anonymous,"},{"time":191000,"text":"getting rent from that knowledge"},{"time":193000,"text":"by sharing it and doing consultancy, writing papers and"},{"time":195000,"text":"publishing them in the papers,"},{"time":197000,"text":"getting invited to the conferences,"},{"time":199000,"text":"getting consultancies and whatever have you."},{"time":202000,"text":"So then, a dilemma rose in the mind that,"},{"time":204000,"text":"if I'm also an exploiter, then this is not right;"},{"time":207000,"text":"life cannot go on like that."},{"time":210000,"text":"And this was a moment of great pain and trauma"},{"time":213000,"text":"because I couldn't live with it any longer."},{"time":217000,"text":"So I did a review of"},{"time":219000,"text":"ethical dilemma and value conflicts and management research,"},{"time":221000,"text":"wrote, read about 100 papers."},{"time":224000,"text":"And I came to the conclusion that"},{"time":226000,"text":"while dilemma is unique,"},{"time":228000,"text":"dilemma is not unique; the solution had to be unique."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"And one day -- I don't know what happened --"},{"time":233000,"text":"while coming back from the office towards home,"},{"time":236000,"text":"maybe I saw a honey bee"},{"time":238000,"text":"or it occurred to my mind that if I only could be like the honey bee,"},{"time":241000,"text":"life would be wonderful."},{"time":243000,"text":"What the honey bee does: it pollinates,"},{"time":246000,"text":"takes nectar from the flower,"},{"time":248000,"text":"pollinates another flower, cross-pollinates."},{"time":250000,"text":"And when it takes the nectar,"},{"time":252000,"text":"the flowers don't feel shortchanged."},{"time":255000,"text":"In fact, they invite the honey bees"},{"time":257000,"text":"through their colors,"},{"time":260000,"text":"and the bees don't keep all the honey for themselves."},{"time":263000,"text":"These are the three guiding principles of the Honey Bee Network:"},{"time":267000,"text":"that whenever we learn something from people"},{"time":269000,"text":"it must be shared with them in their language."},{"time":272000,"text":"They must not remain anonymous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274000,"text":"And I must tell you that after 20 years,"},{"time":277000,"text":"I have not made one percent of change"},{"time":280000,"text":"in the professional practice of this art."},{"time":282000,"text":"That is a great tragedy -- which I'm carrying still with me"},{"time":284000,"text":"and I hope that all of you will carry this with you --"},{"time":286000,"text":"that the profession still legitimizes publication"},{"time":289000,"text":"of knowledge of people without attributing them"},{"time":292000,"text":"by making them anonymous."},{"time":294000,"text":"The research guidelines of U.S. National Academy of Sciences"},{"time":296000,"text":"or Research Councils of the U.K."},{"time":298000,"text":"or of Indian Councils of Science Research"},{"time":300000,"text":"do not require"},{"time":302000,"text":"that whatever you learn from people, you must share back with them."},{"time":305000,"text":"We are talking about an accountable society,"},{"time":307000,"text":"a society that is fair and just,"},{"time":309000,"text":"and we don't even do justice in the knowledge market."},{"time":311000,"text":"And India wants to be a knowledge society."},{"time":313000,"text":"How will it be a knowledge society?"},{"time":315000,"text":"So, obviously, you cannot have two principles of justice,"},{"time":317000,"text":"one for yourself and one for others."},{"time":319000,"text":"It must be the same."},{"time":321000,"text":"You cannot discriminate."},{"time":323000,"text":"You cannot be in favor of your own values,"},{"time":325000,"text":"which are at a distance from"},{"time":327000,"text":"the values that you espouse."},{"time":330000,"text":"So, fairness to one and to the other"},{"time":332000,"text":"is not divisible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334000,"text":"Look at this picture."},{"time":336000,"text":"Can you tell me where has it been taken from,"},{"time":338000,"text":"and what is it meant for? Anybody?"},{"time":341000,"text":"I'm a professor; I must quiz you. (Laughter)"},{"time":345000,"text":"Anybody? Any guess at all?"},{"time":348000,"text":"Pardon? (Audience Member: Rajasthan.)"},{"time":350000,"text":"Anil Gupta: But what has it been used for? What has it been used for?"},{"time":352000,"text":"(Murmuring)"},{"time":354000,"text":"Pardon?"},{"time":356000,"text":"You know, you're so right. We must give him a hand,"},{"time":359000,"text":"because this man knows how insensitive our government is."},{"time":362000,"text":"Look at this. This is the site of the government of India."},{"time":364000,"text":"It invites tourists"},{"time":366000,"text":"to see the shame of our country."},{"time":368000,"text":"I'm so sorry to say that."},{"time":370000,"text":"Is this a beautiful picture"},{"time":372000,"text":"or is it a terrible picture?"},{"time":374000,"text":"It depends upon how you look at the life of the people."},{"time":377000,"text":"If this woman has to carry water on her head"},{"time":379000,"text":"for miles and miles and miles,"},{"time":381000,"text":"you cannot be celebrating that."},{"time":384000,"text":"We should be doing something about it."},{"time":386000,"text":"And let me tell you, with all the science and technology at our command,"},{"time":389000,"text":"millions of women still carry water on their heads."},{"time":392000,"text":"And we do not ask this question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394000,"text":"You must have taken tea in the morning."},{"time":397000,"text":"Think for a minute."},{"time":399000,"text":"The leaves of the tea, plucked from the bushes;"},{"time":402000,"text":"you know what the action is? The action is:"},{"time":404000,"text":"The lady picks up a few leaves, puts them in the basket on the backside."},{"time":407000,"text":"Just do it 10 times;"},{"time":409000,"text":"you will realize the pain in this shoulder."},{"time":411000,"text":"And she does it a few thousand times"},{"time":413000,"text":"every day."},{"time":416000,"text":"The rice that you ate in the lunch, and you will eat today,"},{"time":419000,"text":"is transplanted by women"},{"time":421000,"text":"bending in a very awkward posture,"},{"time":423000,"text":"millions of them,"},{"time":425000,"text":"every season, in the paddy season,"},{"time":427000,"text":"when they transplant paddy"},{"time":430000,"text":"with their feet in the water."},{"time":432000,"text":"And feet in the water will develop fungus,"},{"time":434000,"text":"infections,"},{"time":436000,"text":"and that infection pains"},{"time":438000,"text":"because then other insects bite that point."},{"time":441000,"text":"And every year,"},{"time":443000,"text":"99.9 percent of the paddy is transplanted manually."},{"time":446000,"text":"No machines have been developed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":448000,"text":"So the silence of scientists,"},{"time":450000,"text":"of technologists, of public policy makers,"},{"time":453000,"text":"of the change agent, drew our attention that this is not on, this is not on;"},{"time":456000,"text":"this is not the way society will work."},{"time":458000,"text":"This is not what our parliament would do. You know,"},{"time":461000,"text":"we have a program for employment:"},{"time":463000,"text":"One hundred, 250 million people"},{"time":465000,"text":"have to be given jobs for 100 days by this great country."},{"time":468000,"text":"Doing what? Breaking stones, digging earth."},{"time":471000,"text":"So we asked a question to the parliament:"},{"time":474000,"text":"Do poor have heads?"},{"time":477000,"text":"Do poor have legs, mouth and hands, but no head?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"So Honey Bee Network builds upon the resource in which poor people are rich."},{"time":483000,"text":"And what has happened?"},{"time":485000,"text":"An anonymous, faceless, nameless person"},{"time":488000,"text":"gets in contact with the network,"},{"time":490000,"text":"and then gets an identity."},{"time":492000,"text":"This is what Honey Bee Network is about."},{"time":494000,"text":"And this network grew voluntarily,"},{"time":496000,"text":"continues to be voluntary,"},{"time":498000,"text":"and has tried to map the minds"},{"time":500000,"text":"of millions of people"},{"time":502000,"text":"of our country and other parts of the world who are creative."},{"time":506000,"text":"They could be creative in terms of education,"},{"time":508000,"text":"they may be creative in terms of culture,"},{"time":510000,"text":"they may be creative in terms of institutions;"},{"time":512000,"text":"but a lot of our work is in the field of technological creativity,"},{"time":514000,"text":"the innovations,"},{"time":516000,"text":"either in terms of contemporary innovations,"},{"time":518000,"text":"or in terms of traditional knowledge."},{"time":521000,"text":"And it all begins with curiosity."},{"time":523000,"text":"It all begins with curiosity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525000,"text":"This person, whom we met -- and you will see it on the website,"},{"time":527000,"text":"www.sristi.org -- this tribal person,"},{"time":530000,"text":"he had a wish."},{"time":532000,"text":"And he said, \"If my wish gets fulfilled\" --"},{"time":535000,"text":"somebody was sick and he had to monitor --"},{"time":538000,"text":"\"God, please cure him."},{"time":540000,"text":"And if you cure him, I will get my wall painted.\""},{"time":543000,"text":"And this is what he got painted."},{"time":545000,"text":"Somebody was talking yesterday about Maslowian hierarchy."},{"time":547000,"text":"There could be nothing more wrong than"},{"time":549000,"text":"the Maslowian model of hierarchy of needs"},{"time":551000,"text":"because the poorest people in this country can get enlightenment."},{"time":554000,"text":"Kabir, Rahim, all the great Sufi saints,"},{"time":557000,"text":"they were all poor people,"},{"time":559000,"text":"and they had a great reason. (Applause)"},{"time":561000,"text":"Please do not ever think that"},{"time":563000,"text":"only after meeting your physiological needs and other needs"},{"time":565000,"text":"can you be thinking about your spiritual needs or your enlightenment."},{"time":568000,"text":"Any person anywhere is capable"},{"time":570000,"text":"of rising to that highest point of attainment,"},{"time":573000,"text":"only by the resolve that they have in their mind that they must achieve something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576000,"text":"Look at this."},{"time":578000,"text":"We saw it in Shodh Yatra. Every six months we walk"},{"time":580000,"text":"in different parts of the country."},{"time":582000,"text":"I've walked about 4,000 kilometers in the last 12 years."},{"time":584000,"text":"So on the wayside"},{"time":586000,"text":"we found these dung cakes,"},{"time":588000,"text":"which are used as a fuel."},{"time":590000,"text":"Now, this lady, on the wall of the dung cake heap,"},{"time":593000,"text":"has made a painting."},{"time":595000,"text":"That's the only space she could express her creativity."},{"time":597000,"text":"And she's so marvelous."},{"time":599000,"text":"Look at this lady, Ram Timari Devi,"},{"time":601000,"text":"on a grain bin. In Champaran, we had a Shodh Yatra"},{"time":603000,"text":"and we were walking"},{"time":605000,"text":"in the land where Gandhiji went"},{"time":607000,"text":"to hear about the tragedy, pain"},{"time":609000,"text":"of indigo growers."},{"time":611000,"text":"Bhabi Mahato in Purulia and Bankura."},{"time":613000,"text":"Look at what she has done."},{"time":615000,"text":"The whole wall is her canvas. She's sitting there with a broom."},{"time":618000,"text":"Is she an artisan or an artist?"},{"time":620000,"text":"Obviously she's an artist; she's a creative person."},{"time":622000,"text":"If we can create markets for these artists,"},{"time":625000,"text":"we will not have to employ them for digging earth and breaking stones."},{"time":628000,"text":"They will be paid for what they are good at, not what they're bad at."},{"time":631000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":636000,"text":"Look at what Rojadeen has done."},{"time":638000,"text":"In Motihari in Champaran,"},{"time":640000,"text":"there are a lot of people who sell tea on the shack"},{"time":642000,"text":"and, obviously, there's a limited market for tea."},{"time":645000,"text":"Every morning you have tea, as well as coffee."},{"time":647000,"text":"So he thought, why don't I convert"},{"time":649000,"text":"a pressure cooker into a coffee machine?"},{"time":651000,"text":"So this is a coffee machine. Just takes a few hundred rupees."},{"time":653000,"text":"People bring their own cooker,"},{"time":655000,"text":"he attaches a valve and a steam pipe,"},{"time":658000,"text":"and now he gives you espresso coffee. (Laughter)"},{"time":660000,"text":"Now, this is a real, affordable"},{"time":663000,"text":"coffee percolator that works on gas."},{"time":665000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":667000,"text":"Look at what Sheikh Jahangir has done."},{"time":670000,"text":"A lot of poor people do not have"},{"time":672000,"text":"enough grains to get ground."},{"time":674000,"text":"So this fellow is bringing"},{"time":676000,"text":"a flour-grinding machine on a two-wheeler."},{"time":678000,"text":"If you have 500 grams, 1000, one kilogram,"},{"time":681000,"text":"he will grind it for it for you; the flourmill will not grind such a small quantity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684000,"text":"Please understand the problem of poor people."},{"time":686000,"text":"They have needs which"},{"time":688000,"text":"have to be met efficiently"},{"time":690000,"text":"in terms of energy, in terms of cost, in terms of quality."},{"time":693000,"text":"They don't want second-standard, second-quality outputs."},{"time":696000,"text":"But to be able to give them high-quality output"},{"time":698000,"text":"you need to adapt technology to their needs."},{"time":700000,"text":"And that is what Sheikh Jahangir did."},{"time":702000,"text":"But that's not enough, what he did. Look at what he did here."},{"time":707000,"text":"If you have clothes, and you don't have enough time to wash them,"},{"time":710000,"text":"he brought a washing machine"},{"time":712000,"text":"to your doorstep, mounted on a two-wheeler."},{"time":714000,"text":"So here's a model where"},{"time":716000,"text":"a two-wheeler washing machine ..."},{"time":718000,"text":"He is washing your clothes and drying them at your doorstep."},{"time":720000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":722000,"text":"You bring your water, you bring your soap,"},{"time":725000,"text":"I wash the clothes for you. Charge 50 paisa, one rupee"},{"time":728000,"text":"for you per lot,"},{"time":730000,"text":"and a new business model can emerge."},{"time":732000,"text":"Now, what we need is, we need"},{"time":734000,"text":"people who will be able to scale them up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736000,"text":"Look at this."},{"time":738000,"text":"It looks like a beautiful photograph."},{"time":740000,"text":"But you know what it is? Can anybody guess what it is?"},{"time":742000,"text":"Somebody from India would know, of course."},{"time":744000,"text":"It's a tawa."},{"time":747000,"text":"It's a hot plate made of clay."},{"time":751000,"text":"Now, what is the beauty in it?"},{"time":754000,"text":"When you have a non-stick pan,"},{"time":756000,"text":"it costs about,"},{"time":758000,"text":"maybe, 250 rupees,"},{"time":760000,"text":"five dollars, six dollars."},{"time":762000,"text":"This is less than a dollar"},{"time":764000,"text":"and this is non-stick;"},{"time":766000,"text":"it is coated with one of these"},{"time":768000,"text":"food-grade materials."},{"time":770000,"text":"And the best part is that,"},{"time":772000,"text":"while you use a costly non-stick pan,"},{"time":774000,"text":"you eat the so-called Teflon"},{"time":776000,"text":"or Teflon-like material"},{"time":778000,"text":"because after some time the stuff disappears. Where has it gone?"},{"time":780000,"text":"It has gone in your stomach. It was not meant for that. (Laughter)"},{"time":783000,"text":"You know? But here"},{"time":785000,"text":"in this clay hot plate,"},{"time":788000,"text":"it will never go into your stomach."},{"time":790000,"text":"So it is better, it is safer;"},{"time":792000,"text":"it is affordable, it is energy-efficient."},{"time":795000,"text":"In other words, solutions by the poor people need not be cheaper,"},{"time":798000,"text":"need not be, so-called, jugaad, need not be some kind of makeshift arrangement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801000,"text":"They have to be better, they have to be more efficient,"},{"time":803000,"text":"they have to be affordable."},{"time":805000,"text":"And that is what Mansukh Bhai Prajapati has done."},{"time":807000,"text":"He has designed this plate with a handle."},{"time":810000,"text":"And now with one dollar,"},{"time":812000,"text":"you can afford a better alternative"},{"time":814000,"text":"than the people market is offering you."},{"time":816000,"text":"This lady, she developed"},{"time":818000,"text":"a herbal pesticide formulation."},{"time":820000,"text":"We filed the patent for her,"},{"time":822000,"text":"the National Innovation Foundation."},{"time":824000,"text":"And who knows? Somebody will license this technology"},{"time":827000,"text":"and develop marketable products,"},{"time":830000,"text":"and she would get revenue."},{"time":832000,"text":"Now, let me mention one thing:"},{"time":834000,"text":"I think we need a polycentric model of development,"},{"time":836000,"text":"where a large number of initiatives in different parts of the country,"},{"time":839000,"text":"in different parts of the world,"},{"time":841000,"text":"would solve the needs of locality"},{"time":843000,"text":"in a very efficient and adaptive manner."},{"time":845000,"text":"Higher the local fit,"},{"time":847000,"text":"greater is the chance of scaling up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":849000,"text":"In the scaling up,"},{"time":851000,"text":"there's an inherent inadequacy"},{"time":853000,"text":"to match the needs of the local people,"},{"time":856000,"text":"point by point, with the supply that you're making."},{"time":858000,"text":"So why are people willing to adjust with that mismatch?"},{"time":861000,"text":"Things can scale up, and they have scaled up."},{"time":864000,"text":"For example, cell phones: We have 400 million cellphones in this country."},{"time":867000,"text":"Now, it is possible that I use only two buttons on the cellphone,"},{"time":870000,"text":"only three options on the cellphone."},{"time":872000,"text":"It has 300 options, I'm paying for 300; I'm using only three"},{"time":875000,"text":"but I'm willing to live with it, therefore it is scaling up."},{"time":878000,"text":"But if I had to get a match to match,"},{"time":880000,"text":"obviously, I would need a different design of a cellphone."},{"time":883000,"text":"So what we're saying is that scalability"},{"time":885000,"text":"should not become an enemy of sustainability."},{"time":887000,"text":"There must be a place in the world"},{"time":889000,"text":"for solutions that are only relevant for a locality,"},{"time":892000,"text":"and yet, one can be able to fund them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":896000,"text":"One of the greatest studies that we've been finding is"},{"time":898000,"text":"that many times investors would ask this question --"},{"time":900000,"text":"\"What is a scalable model?\" --"},{"time":902000,"text":"as if the need of a community, which is only"},{"time":904000,"text":"located in a space and time"},{"time":906000,"text":"and has those needs only located in those places,"},{"time":909000,"text":"has no legitimate right to get them for free"},{"time":911000,"text":"because it's not part of a larger scale."},{"time":913000,"text":"So either you sub-optimize your needs to a larger scale"},{"time":915000,"text":"or else you remain out."},{"time":917000,"text":"Now, the eminent model, the long-tail model"},{"time":920000,"text":"tells you that small sales"},{"time":922000,"text":"of a large number of books, for example,"},{"time":924000,"text":"having only a few copies sold"},{"time":926000,"text":"can still be a viable model."},{"time":928000,"text":"And we must find a mechanism where"},{"time":930000,"text":"people will pool in the portfolio, will invest in the portfolio,"},{"time":933000,"text":"where different innovations will go to"},{"time":935000,"text":"a small number of people in their localities,"},{"time":937000,"text":"and yet, the overall platform of the model will become viable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":939000,"text":"Look at what he is doing."},{"time":941000,"text":"Saidullah Sahib is an amazing man."},{"time":944000,"text":"At the age of 70,"},{"time":946000,"text":"he is linking up something very creative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":949000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":955000,"text":"Saidullah Sahib: I couldn't wait for the boat."},{"time":962000,"text":"I had to meet my love."},{"time":972000,"text":"My desperation made me an innovator."},{"time":983000,"text":"Even love needs help from technology."},{"time":992000,"text":"Innovation is the light of my wife, Noor."},{"time":996000,"text":"New inventions are the passion of my life."},{"time":1002000,"text":"My technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1005000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1011000,"text":"AG: Saidulluh Sahib is"},{"time":1013000,"text":"in Motihari, again in Champaran."},{"time":1015000,"text":"Wonderful human being,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"but he stills sells, at this age,"},{"time":1021000,"text":"honey on a cycle to earn his livelihood,"},{"time":1023000,"text":"because we haven't been able to convince the water park people,"},{"time":1026000,"text":"the lake people, in [unclear] operations."},{"time":1029000,"text":"And we have not been able to convince the fire brigade people"},{"time":1031000,"text":"in Mumbai -- where there was a flood a few years ago"},{"time":1033000,"text":"and people had to walk 20 kilometers, wading in the water --"},{"time":1036000,"text":"that, look, you should have this cycle in your fire brigade office"},{"time":1038000,"text":"because you can then go to those lanes"},{"time":1040000,"text":"where your buses will not go, where your transport will not go."},{"time":1043000,"text":"So we have not yet cracked the problem"},{"time":1045000,"text":"of making it available as a rescue device,"},{"time":1048000,"text":"as a vending device during the floods in eastern India,"},{"time":1050000,"text":"when you have to deliver things to people"},{"time":1052000,"text":"in different islands"},{"time":1054000,"text":"where they're marooned."},{"time":1056000,"text":"But the idea has a merit. The idea has a merit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1059000,"text":"What has Appachan done? Appachan, unfortunately, is no more,"},{"time":1062000,"text":"but he has left behind a message."},{"time":1064000,"text":"A very powerful message"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1069000,"text":"Appachan: I watch the world wake up every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1072000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1087000,"text":"It's not that a coconut fell on my head,"},{"time":1089000,"text":"and I came upon this idea."},{"time":1096000,"text":"With no money to fund my studies,"},{"time":1099000,"text":"I scaled new heights."},{"time":1103000,"text":"Now, they call me the local Spiderman."},{"time":1115000,"text":"My technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1117000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1120000,"text":"AG: Many of you"},{"time":1122000,"text":"might not realize and believe"},{"time":1125000,"text":"that we have sold this product internationally --"},{"time":1127000,"text":"what I call a G2G model,"},{"time":1129000,"text":"grassroots to global."},{"time":1131000,"text":"And a professor in the University of Massachusetts,"},{"time":1133000,"text":"in the zoology department,"},{"time":1135000,"text":"bought this climber because she wanted"},{"time":1138000,"text":"to study the insect diversity"},{"time":1140000,"text":"of the top of the tree canopy."},{"time":1143000,"text":"And this device makes it possible"},{"time":1145000,"text":"for her to take samples from a larger number of palms,"},{"time":1147000,"text":"rather than only a few,"},{"time":1149000,"text":"because otherwise she had to make a big platform"},{"time":1151000,"text":"and then climb her [unclear] would climb on that."},{"time":1153000,"text":"So, you know, we are advancing the frontiers of science."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1155000,"text":"Remya Jose has developed ..."},{"time":1157000,"text":"you can go to the YouTube and find India Innovates"},{"time":1159000,"text":"and then you will find these videos."},{"time":1161000,"text":"Innovation by her when she was in class 10th:"},{"time":1163000,"text":"a washing machine-cum-exercising machine."},{"time":1165000,"text":"Mr. Kharai who is a physically challenged person,"},{"time":1168000,"text":"one and a half foot height, only."},{"time":1170000,"text":"But he has modified a two-wheeler so that he can get autonomy"},{"time":1173000,"text":"and freedom and flexibility."},{"time":1176000,"text":"This innovation is from the slums of Rio."},{"time":1179000,"text":"And this person, Mr. Ubirajara."},{"time":1181000,"text":"We were talking about, my friends in Brazil,"},{"time":1183000,"text":"how we scale up this model in China and Brazil."},{"time":1185000,"text":"And we have a very vibrant network in China, particularly,"},{"time":1188000,"text":"but also emerging in Brazil and other parts of the world."},{"time":1191000,"text":"This stand on the front wheel, you will not find on any cycle."},{"time":1194000,"text":"India and China have the largest number of cycles."},{"time":1196000,"text":"But this innovation emerged in Brazil."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1199000,"text":"The point is, none of us should be parochial,"},{"time":1202000,"text":"none of us should be so nationalistic to believe"},{"time":1204000,"text":"that all good ideas will come only from our country."},{"time":1206000,"text":"No, we have to have the humility to learn"},{"time":1209000,"text":"from knowledge of economically poor people, wherever they are."},{"time":1212000,"text":"And look at this whole range of cycle-based innovations:"},{"time":1215000,"text":"cycle that's a sprayer, cycle that"},{"time":1217000,"text":"generates energy from the shocks on the road."},{"time":1219000,"text":"I can't change the condition of the road,"},{"time":1220000,"text":"but I can make the cycle run faster."},{"time":1222000,"text":"That is what Kanak Das has done."},{"time":1224000,"text":"And in South Africa,"},{"time":1226000,"text":"we had taken our innovators,"},{"time":1228000,"text":"and many of us had gone there share with the colleagues in South Africa"},{"time":1231000,"text":"as to how innovation can become"},{"time":1233000,"text":"a means of liberation"},{"time":1235000,"text":"from the drudgery that people have."},{"time":1237000,"text":"And this is a donkey cart which they modified."},{"time":1239000,"text":"There's an axle here, of 30, 40 kg,"},{"time":1241000,"text":"serving no purpose."},{"time":1243000,"text":"Remove it, the cart needs one donkey less."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1246000,"text":"This is in China. This girl needed a breathing apparatus."},{"time":1249000,"text":"These three people in the village"},{"time":1251000,"text":"sat down and decided to think,"},{"time":1253000,"text":"\"How do we elongate the life of this girl of our village?\""},{"time":1255000,"text":"They were not related to her, but they tried to find out,"},{"time":1257000,"text":"\"How can we use ... \""},{"time":1260000,"text":"They used a cycle, they put together a breathing apparatus."},{"time":1263000,"text":"And this breathing apparatus now saved the life,"},{"time":1265000,"text":"and she's very welcome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1267000,"text":"There's a whole range of innovations that we have."},{"time":1269000,"text":"A car, which runs on compressed air"},{"time":1272000,"text":"with six paisa per kilometer."},{"time":1274000,"text":"Assam, Kanak Gogoi."},{"time":1276000,"text":"And you would not find this car in U.S. or Europe,"},{"time":1278000,"text":"but this is available in India."},{"time":1280000,"text":"Now, this lady, she used to do the winding of the yarn"},{"time":1283000,"text":"for Pochampally Saree."},{"time":1285000,"text":"In one day, 18,000 times,"},{"time":1287000,"text":"she had to do this winding"},{"time":1289000,"text":"to generate two sarees."},{"time":1291000,"text":"This is what her son has done after seven years of struggle."},{"time":1294000,"text":"She said, \"Change your profession.\""},{"time":1296000,"text":"He said, \"I can't. This is the only thing I know, but I'll invent a machine,"},{"time":1298000,"text":"which will solve your problem.\""},{"time":1300000,"text":"And this is what he did, a sewing machine in Uttar Pradesh."},{"time":1302000,"text":"So, this is what SRISTI is saying:"},{"time":1304000,"text":"\"Give me a place to stand, and I will move the world.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1307000,"text":"I will just tell you that we are also doing a competition among children"},{"time":1310000,"text":"for creativity, a whole range of things."},{"time":1313000,"text":"We have sold things all over the world,"},{"time":1315000,"text":"from Ethiopia to Turkey to U.S. to wherever."},{"time":1318000,"text":"Products have gone to the market, a few."},{"time":1320000,"text":"These are the people whose knowledge made"},{"time":1322000,"text":"this Herbavate cream for eczema possible."},{"time":1324000,"text":"And here, a company which licensed this herbal pesticide"},{"time":1326000,"text":"put a photograph of the innovator on the packing"},{"time":1328000,"text":"so that every time a user uses it,"},{"time":1330000,"text":"it asks the user, \"You can also be an innovator."},{"time":1332000,"text":"If you have an idea, send it back to us.\""},{"time":1335000,"text":"So, creativity counts, knowledge matters,"},{"time":1338000,"text":"innovations transform, incentives inspire."},{"time":1341000,"text":"And incentives: not just material, but also non-material incentives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1344000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1346000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}